data.description: Who wants a pool without the maintenance?   Come see this amazing home with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and a 2 car garage.  Huge master and bath and 2nd floor laundry.  And that's just the start of this great home!  This lovely Dover neighborhood has sidewalks for evening walks and It has very inviting landscaping with a brand new fenced back yard.  When you enter the house, the hardwood floors and large foyer are the perfect place to leave your day behind.  You can relax in your large living room with a cozy gas fireplace, open to your kitchen (all appliances are included) with island and pantry space.  Room for family and friends to gather in the dining area or just slip through the sliding glass doors to the outside patio with lots of privacy.  At the end of your day, the Master Bedroom will not disappoint.  HUGE space with enough room for your king size bed, lots of furniture AND a sitting area, plus a large walk in closet and big en suite bath.  Set up an appointment today!
